             Asked at: Amazon, Microsoft

  [C][ ] (E) Count the number of uppercase and lowercase letters in a string.
             Asked at: TCS, Wipro, Capgemini

  [C][ ] (E) Find the longest word in a sentence.
             Asked at: TCS, Wipro, Zoho

