  [C][ ] (E) Count occurrences of a word in a sentence (case-insensitive).
             Asked at: TCS, Wipro, Zoho

  [C][ ] (E) Given string, print all characters in it that appear exactly once.
             Asked at: TCS, Wipro, Amazon

  [C][ ] (E) Check if string contains only digits.
             Asked at: TCS, Wipro, Capgemini

  [C][ ] (E) Caesar cipher: shift characters by K positions in alphabet.
             Wrap around: 'z' + 1 = 'a'.
             Asked at: TCS, Capgemini, Zoho

  [C][ ] (E) Given two strings, find the number of positions where
             they have the same character.
